                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.00/2145.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Minister for Foreign Affairs of Nicaragua</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your cordial salutation received with thanks. Accept my sincere good wishes for
                    the continued prosperity of Nicaragua.</p>
                <closer>(For the Secretary of State.) <lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">A. A. Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
